snippet.textDisplay:
For all the people saying that the 7 others should have been mentioned too, yes I agree. But the Grammy's were hosted at the Staples Center, where Kobe played basketball for 20 years, made his career, and was such an amazing father, icon, role model, and was known world wide for inspiring people to be who they are. The other victims Alyssa, Payton, Gigi and everybody else, had their life in front of them, it's so sad to see them leave us so young and talented.
Rest In Peace :
Alyssa Altobelli
Keri Altobelli
John Altobelli
Christina Mauser
Ara Zobayan
Payton Chester
Sarah Chester
Gianna Bryant
and, Kobe Bryant.
